    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-07-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-07-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="152"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d152">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00R296/4499</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Egyptian Chargé</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Aly Ismail Bey</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-15">July 15,
                            1931</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: I have the honour to inform Your
                    Excellency that the Royal Egyptian Government has definitely accepted today the
                    suspension of her part in the German reparations, in conformity with the plan of
                    President Hoover. Inspired by its duties of international solidarity, the
                    Government submitted that acceptance to both Houses, namely the Chamber of
                    Deputies and the Senate, which welcomed the motion by unanimous applause.</p>
                <pb facs="0317" n="203" xml:id="pg_203"/>
                <p>I am particularly gratified to inform Your Excellency, also, that the Leaders of
                    the different parties in the Chamber of Deputies, including the Leader of the
                    opposition, supported the Government and congratulated themselves for such an
                    opportunity as would permit Egypt to prove its desire to share in the general
                    cooperation towards peace and economic stability.</p>
                <p>Availing myself [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alt Ismail Bey</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
